metadata.name: Me
metadata.description:
This is 1st NFT in a collection of 8 photographs that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

Photo: 5330x6995 px

I'm Olgeya, I love to reincarnate, to live my life with different emotions.
My photos are my reflection frozen in the moment, I am like a fly in amber, only I am frozen not for ages, but every time I melt my amber captivity and reborn in a new image, in a new sense of myself.
